  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Waldorf Training to three teachers in Kenya.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Based in the UNESCO Statistics from 2016, less than 10% of women in Kenya have the opportunity to go to university, and with this fundraising project we will pay the complete fees of Rudolf Steiner training to one teacher, finish to pay the partial fees of the two other teachers from Hai Africa School and buy pedagogy books providing them with high quality education in order to impact the education of  39 kids from our kindergarten. In addition, the funds raised will also help cover 1 year rent.</narrative>
  </description>
